S.FORM: I 1944 a miheca saka 9 folad saka 28 a romi'ad masofoc ci Miloš Zeman , malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Czechia anini i ci Miloš Zeman, patirengan a romi'ad i 2013 a miheca saka 3 folad saka 8 a romi'ad.
